Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san {\i0}was crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,See, if a pillar goes there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like this city is going to just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,If everything disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,...will Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s sorrow disappear too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of staying over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}is helping me out with dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really good with the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh stop it, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:13.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:03:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The stewed potatoes taste really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you. Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Ruko, c'mon and eat some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}... Doesn't she have to go home...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Whew! The bath felt really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Stuffed myself with food, and took\Na hot bath. Now I'm Ener Charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Orichalcum, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,--Y-Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}... Th-That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--Take this, and that!\N--Y-Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}... Th-That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I said horrible things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're thinking, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:18.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't worry about it.\NIt doesn't bother me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle against her... against Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...have someone that I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,...it will never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,How would you know?\NI mean, you are cute, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it just won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,But if it did, I could like him\Njust like anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be...? Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, the person you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...is it Kazu--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it feels like to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you get really excited, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Excited? Excited in battle! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Received E-mail: Kazuki"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"We had your favorite pancake meal for dinner."\N"I kept some for you, so warm them up tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Received E-mail: Akira"\N"Hey there!! Introduce me to your friend"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Received E-mail: Akira"\N"Want to battle. I want to battle Ru-ru"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Received E-mail: Akira" "Stop ignoring me.\NDon't ignore me, no teasing here, never!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,--Bye-bye!\N--See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Gone home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san {\i0}made notes about\Ndecks and battle progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So I decided to copy that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea. You can look at\Nyour deck outside of the box with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I would like to be friends with Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,With Yuzuki-{\i1}san {\i0}too! You're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean me? Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,T-Two friends? At once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS is so... wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was battling Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}, it was so\Npainful that I thought I was going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Doing battle as a Selector\Nis going to be painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought this was natural,\Nsince you're trying to attain your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But, after battling Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}, I sincerely\Nenjoyed the battle from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's play a game of WIXOSS\Nto show we're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But, if Selectors battle each other,\Nsomeone's wish will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}and gals aren't in\Nthe deck, we can battle like any other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Have fun, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn, Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to play too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We did rock-paper-scissors, right? You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll summon Baromet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Baromet's power is 7000, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...won't it be beaten by Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nability after her LRIG Grows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruko! Stop saying stuff from the sidelines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama wants to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama and Ruko are really alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess Hitoe's wish already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need to battle any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that means you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Not that, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. I called you by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm calling you by name already too, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I can feel your friendship. It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you call us\Nby name too, Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call you "Hitoe," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... Then, R-Ruko... Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That feels so weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh, come now.\N--So, weird...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Hitoe smile like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I wasn't Hitoe's LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Ru. Tama likes being Ru's LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama and Ruko are friends after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo... Tama is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... Tama doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You really like WIXOSS, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, I like it. Really like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Right! At the entrance gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like Akira is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean the model, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You're kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... Ru-ru went home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so meanie to break a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira knows Kominato-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's Kominato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare she make Akira sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru didn't do anything bad.\NI'll come back again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:57.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But, what should I do if\Nshe goes home early again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be great if someone could\Nlet Akira know about Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's so pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll let you know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you...! Well, I have a shoot\NI need to go to now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Do your best!\N--See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't be running from\NKazuki forever, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like Akira came to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You're pretty strong, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then! Milk tea for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma wants some sweet bean soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:59.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I come back and\Nall of a sudden I'm a peon, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry-hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko... you look happier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Next, Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}is going to battle Grandma.\NWhoever loses has to clean the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Grandma! You're too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish we could battle and\Nhave fun like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...battling with Tama is a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just for play...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,...but in a battle field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A battle against Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:44.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that's a battle for everyone's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have a wish,\Nso I shouldn't get too involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry! It's my turn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}is looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,She really wants to battle you, Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,She's so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose to Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nit doesn't mean much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, so don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll probably say all sorts of bad things\Nabout you, but don't let that get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,The moment it does, she'll get the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't have friends in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ru-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you. Let's go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I just got\Nan email from Aki-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She invited us to come down\Nto the photo studio with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she'd show us around\Nthe studio if we went together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,We may even get to meet Iona--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:05.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't go. We have\Nsomething to do after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not invited, so shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Ru-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no stronger bond of\Nfriendship than a mutual enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"There is no stronger bond of friendship"\NOkay that will be it for today. The remainder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,"than a mutual enemy."\NOkay that will be it for today. The remainder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Can students from the other\Nclass please not come in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We're leaving anyways! Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey girls, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut it! Scrub-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Scrub-face...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let her get away!\NSend an email to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:02.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I found them, {\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,They're really persistent...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuzuki, it's okay. I can go and battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember when I told you that\NI didn't know what you were thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I do know one thing now for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That you really like WIXOSS battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling Akira is going to be painful... It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling her may make you hate WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The freshmen said they saw them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw them outside, so you stay put here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki is really worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I get hurt or am in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,...I want to battle Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru and Tama are same!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Want to battle Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama is... scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...like Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Ruko is thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We brought her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! Seriously? Shucks, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything for Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You're awesome! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Ru-ru? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I got a photo shoot to do, so leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,W-We thought you were\Ngoing to show us around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is no place for uglies like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No one will get in our way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's start our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle against Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:20:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, if you're going to battle, let me in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Stop trying to take my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I can battle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to battle me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, um... just a moment. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--Like, just wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--Just hurry up! Everyone is waiting...\N--Like, just wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Why... are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanted to battle, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanted to battle Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyone would have been fine\Nso long as you had your WIXOSS battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,A serious battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...do it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,A person without a wish participating\Nin WIXOSS as a Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Blasphemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There may be Selectors there, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I notice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured I could tie my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop saying weird things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,...kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Invalidated Vow."
